        <label class="text-lg inline-block mb-2"
          >Microblading Consultation</label
        >
        <div>
          <p
            class="text-ellipsis italic overflow-hidden line-clamp-3 text-sm text-balance mb-2"
          >
            In this appointment, we will talk about the microblading process,
            preparation, service, and healing. You will get a rough draft "brow
            map" and see what your semi-permenant, low-maintenance brow shape
            will be.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm">Free ・ 1 hr 10 min</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="service-block rounded-tl rounded-tr-[1rem] rounded-br rounded-bl-[1rem] p-3 mb-2 border border-transparent hover:border-rose-gold-500 dark:hover:border-ivory-rose-500 transition-all"
      >
        <label class="text-lg inline-block mb-2">Eyebrow Microblade</label>
        <div>
          <p
            class="text-ellipsis italic overflow-hidden line-clamp-3 text-sm text-balance mb-2"
          >
            This semi-permanent eyebrow shape will make getting ready so much
            easier! Your brows will be customized to your face shape, brow
            bones, and features.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm">$350.00 ・ 2 hr 30 min</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="service-block rounded-tl rounded-tr-[1rem] rounded-br rounded-bl-[1rem] p-3 mb-2 border border-transparent hover:border-rose-gold-500 dark:hover:border-ivory-rose-500 transition-all"
      >
        <label class="text-lg inline-block mb-2">Lash Removal</label>
        <div>
          <p
            class="text-ellipsis italic overflow-hidden line-clamp-3 text-sm text-balance mb-2"
          >
            Removal of current lash extensions
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm">$30.00 ・ 40 min</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="service-block rounded-tl rounded-tr-[1rem] rounded-br rounded-bl-[1rem] p-3 mb-2 border border-transparent hover:border-rose-gold-500 dark:hover:border-ivory-rose-500 transition-all"
      >
        <label class="text-lg inline-block mb-2"
          >Microblade 6 week touch up</label
        >
        <div>
          <p
            class="text-ellipsis italic overflow-hidden line-clamp-3 text-sm text-balance mb-2"
          >
            Touch up from initial microblade appointment at Moxie Beauty Studio
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm">$50.00 ・ 1 hr 15 min</p>
